dmca.title: Battle of the Goddesses
dmca.body:
Hi, I am writing to inform you that you are using my trademark. I am the
owner of U.S. trademark #3,028,714 for Web Goddess and would appreciate it
if you would no longer use my trademark on your web pages.

Please find attached a copy of my trademark registration or to view it
online go to:
http://www.web-goddess.com/WG.pdf

Thank you,

[private]
Web Goddess
